awkins]] \u2013 ''[[Happy-Go-Lucky (2008 film)|Happy-Go-Lucky]]'' as Pauline \"Poppy\" Cross\n* [[Melissa Leo]] \u2013 ''[[Frozen River]]'' as Ray Eddy\n* [[Meryl Streep]] \u2013 ''[[Doubt (2008 film)|Doubt]]'' as Sister Aloysius Beauvier\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[Heath Ledger]] \u2013 ''[[The Dark Knight (film)|The Dark Knight]]'' as [[The Joker (The Dark Knight)|The Joker]]'''\n* [[Robert Downey Jr.]] \u2013 ''[[Tropic Thunder]]'' as Kirk Lazarus\n* [[James Franco]] \u2013 ''[[Pineapple Express (film)|Pineapple Express]]'' as Saul Silver\n* [[Eddie Marsan]] \u2013 ''[[Happy-Go-Lucky (2008 film)|Happy-Go-Lucky]]'' as Scott\n* [[Michael Shannon]] \u2013 ''[[Revolutionary Road (film)|Revolutionary Road]]'' as John Givings, Jr.\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Marisa Tomei]] \u2013 ''[[The Wrestler (2008 film)|The Wrestler]]'' as Pam / Cassidy'''\n* [[Amy Adams]] \u2013 ''[[Doubt (2008 film)|Doubt]]'' as Sister James\n* [[Elizabeth Banks]] \u2013 ''[[W. (film)|W.]]'' as [[Laura Bush]]\n* [[Pen\u00e9lope Cruz]] \u2013 ''[[Vicky Cristina Barcelona]]'' as Mar\u00eda Elena\n* [[Rosemarie DeWitt]] \u2013 ''[[Rachel Getting Married]]'' as Rachel Buchman\n\n===Best Cast===\n'''''[[Frost/Nixon (film)|Frost/Nixon]]'''''\n* ''[[Burn After Reading]]''\n* ''[[Rachel Getting Married]]''\n* ''[[Revolutionary Road (film)|Revolutionary Road]]''\n* ''[[Tropic Thunder]]''\n\n===Best Newcomer===\n'''[[Martin McDonagh]] \u2013 ''[[In Bruges]]'''''\n* [[Rosemarie DeWitt]] \u2013 ''[[Rachel Getting Married]]'' as Rachel Buchman\n* [[Rebecca Hall]] \u2013 ''[[Frost/Nixon (film)|Frost/Nixon]]'' and ''[[Vicky Cristina Barcelona]]'' as Caroline Cushing and Vicky\n* [[Danny McBride (actor)|Danny McBride]] \u2013 ''[[Pineapple Express (film)|Pineapple Express]]'' as Red\n* [[Dev Patel]] \u2013 ''[[Slumdog Millionaire]]'' as [[Jamal Malik (character)|Jamal Malik]]\n* Catinca Untaru \u2013 ''[[The Fall (2006 film)|The Fall]]'' as Alexandria\n\n==2009==\n\n===Best Film===\n'''''[[Up (2009 film)|Up]]'''''\n* ''[[500 Days of Summer|(500) Days of Summer]]''\n* ''[[The Hurt Locker]]''\n* ''[[Inglourious Basterds]]''\n* ''[[Up in the Air (2009 film)|Up in the Air]]''\n\n===Best Director===\n'''[[Pete Docter]] \u2013 ''[[Up (2009 film)|Up]]'''''\n* [[Kathryn Bigelow]] \u2013 ''[[The Hurt Locker]]''\n* [[Jason Reitman]] \u2013 ''[[Up in the Air (2009 film)|Up in the Air]]''\n* [[Quentin Tarantino]] \u2013 ''[[Inglourious Basterds]]''\n* [[Marc Webb]] \u2013 ''[[500 Days of Summer|(500) Days of Summer]]''\n\n===Best Actor===\n'''[[Colin Firth]] \u2013 ''[[A Single Man]]'' George Falconer'''\n* [[George Clooney]] \u2013 ''[[Up in the Air (2009 film)|Up in the Air]]'' as Ryan Bingham\n* [[Matt Damon]] \u2013 ''[[The Informant!]]'' as Mark Whitacre\n* [[Joseph Gordon-Levitt]] \u2013 ''[[500 Days of Summer|(500) Days of Summer]]'' as Tom Hansen\n* [[Sam Rockwell]] \u2013 ''[[Moon (film)|Moon]]'' as Sam Bell\n\n===Best Actress===\n'''[[Gabourey Sidibe]] \u2013 ''[[Precious (film)|Precious]]'' as Claireece \"Precious\" Jones'''\n* [[Alison Lohman]] \u2013 ''[[Drag Me to Hell]]'' as Christine Brown\n* [[Carey Mulligan]] \u2013 ''[[An Education]]'' as Jenny Melor\n* [[Saoirse Ronan]] \u2013 ''[[The Lovely Bones (film)|The Lovely Bones]]'' as Susie Salmon\n* [[Meryl Streep]] \u2013 ''[[Julie & Julia]]'' as [[Julia Child]]\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[Christoph Waltz]] \u2013 ''[[Inglourious Basterds]]'' as [[Hans Landa|Col. Hans Landa]]'''\n* [[Woody Harrelson]] \u2013 ''[[The Messenger (2009 film)|The Messenger]]'' as Capt. Tony Stone\n* [[Woody Harrelson]] \u2013 ''[[Zombieland]]'' as Tallahassee\n* [[Christian McKay]] \u2013 ''[[Me and Orson Welles]]'' as [[Orson Welles]]\n* [[Stanley Tucci]] \u2013 ''[[The Lovely Bones (film)|The Lovely Bones]]'' as George Harvey\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Mo'Nique]] \u2013 ''[[Precious (film)|Precious]]'' as Mary Lee Johnston'''\n* [[Marion Cotillard]] \u2013 ''[[Nine (2009 live-action film)|Nine]]'' 