ips]]'' as [[Abduwali Muse]]\n* [[James Franco]] \u2013 ''[[Spring Breakers]]'' as Alien\n* [[Matthew McConaughey]] \u2013 ''[[Mud (2012 film)|Mud]]'' as Mud\n* [[Stanley Tucci]] \u2013 ''[[The Hunger Games: Catching Fire]]'' as Caesar Flickerman\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Scarlett Johansson]] \u2013 ''[[Her (film)|Her]]'' as Samantha (voice)'''\n* [[Jennifer Lawrence]] \u2013 ''[[American Hustle]]'' as Rosalyn Rosenfeld (based on Cynthia Marie Weinberg)\n* [[Lupita Nyong'o]] \u2013 ''[[12 Years a Slave (film)|12 Years a Slave]]'' as [[Patsey]]\n* [[Julia Roberts]] \u2013 ''[[August: Osage County (film)|August: Osage County]]'' as Barbara Weston-Fordham\n* [[June Squibb]] \u2013 ''[[Nebraska (film)|Nebraska]]'' as Kate Grant\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[American Hustle]]'''''\n* ''[[12 Years a Slave (film)|12 Years a Slave]]''\n* ''[[August: Osage County (film)|August: Osage County]]''\n* ''[[Blue Jasmine]]''\n* ''[[The Wolf of Wall Street (2013 film)|The Wolf of Wall Street]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Brie Larson]] \u2013 ''[[Short Term 12]]'' (actress)'''\n* [[Lake Bell]] \u2013 ''[[In a World]]'' (actress, screenplay, director)\n* [[Ryan Coogler]] \u2013 ''[[Fruitvale Station]]'' (screenplay, director)\n* [[Destin Cretton]] \u2013 ''[[Short Term 12]]'' (screenplay, director)\n* [[Michael B. Jordan]] \u2013 ''[[Fruitvale Station]]'' (actor)\n\n===Best Screenplay===\n'''[[Spike Jonze]] \u2013 ''[[Her (film)|Her]]'''''\n* [[Destin Cretton]] \u2013 ''[[Short Term 12]]''\n* [[Richard Linklater]], [[Julie Delpy]], and [[Ethan Hawke]] \u2013 ''[[Before Midnight (2013 film)|Before Midnight]]''\n* [[David O. Russell]] and [[Eric Warren Singer]] \u2013 ''[[American Hustle]]''\n* [[Terence Winter]] \u2013 ''[[The Wolf of Wall Street (2013 film)|The Wolf of Wall Street]]''\n\n===Best Documentary Film===\n'''''[[Stories We Tell]]'''''\n* ''[[Blackfish (film)|Blackfish]]''\n* ''[[The Act of Killing]]''\n* ''[[The Square (2013 film)|The Square]]''\