h Hamilton (actor)|Josh Hamilton]] \u2013 ''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eighth Grade]]'' as Mark Day'''\n* [[Mahershala Ali]] \u2013 ''[[Green Book (film)|Green Book]]'' as [[Don Shirley]]\n* [[Sam Elliott]] \u2013 ''[[A Star Is Born (2018 film)|A Star Is Born]]'' as Bobby Maine\n* [[Richard E. Grant]] \u2013 ''[[Can You Ever Forgive Me? (film)|Can You Ever Forgive Me?]]'' as Jack Hock\n* [[Jesse Plemons]] \u2013 ''[[Game Night (film)|Game Night]]'' as Gary Kingsbury\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Regina King]] \u2013 ''[[If Beale Street Could Talk (film)|If Beale Street Could Talk]]'' as Sharon Rivers'''\n* [[Amy Adams]] \u2013 ''[[Vice (2018 film)|Vice]]'' as [[Lynne Cheney]]\n* [[Thomasin McKenzie]] \u2013 ''[[Leave No Trace (film)|Leave No Trace]]'' as Tom\n* [[Emma Stone]] \u2014 ''[[The Favourite (film)|The Favourite]]'' as [[Abigail Masham, Baroness Masham|Abigail Hill]]\n* [[Rachel Weisz]] \u2013 ''[[The Favourite (film)|The Favourite]]'' as [[Sarah Churchill, Duchess of Marlborough|Sarah Churchill]]\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[Vice (2018 film)|Vice]]'''''\n* ''[[Crazy Rich Asians (film)|Crazy Rich Asians]]''\n* ''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eighth Grade]]''\n* ''[[The Favourite (film)|The Favourite]]''\n* ''[[Roma (2018 film)|Roma]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Bo Burnham]] \u2013 ''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eighth Grade]]'' (writer/director)'''\n* Rafael Casal and [[Daveed Diggs]] \u2013 ''[[Blindspotting]]'' (writers/actors)\n* [[Elsie Fisher]] \u2013 ''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eighth Grade]]'' (actress)\n* [[Lady Gaga]] \u2013 ''[[A Star Is Born (2018 film)|A Star Is Born]]'' (actress)\n* [[Boots Riley]] \u2013 ''[[Sorry to Bother You (film)|Sorry to Bother You]]'' (writer/director)\n\n===Best Screenplay===\n'''Brian Hayes Currie, [[Peter Farrelly]], and [[Nick Vallelonga]] \u2013 ''[[Green Book (film)|Green Book]]'' (TIE)''' <br />\n'''[[Adam McKay]] \u2013 ''[[Vice (2018 film)|Vice]]'' (TIE)'''\n* [[Bo Burnham]] \u2013 ''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eigh