 Adult (film)|Young Adult]]'' as Mavis Gary\n\n===Best Supporting Actor===\n'''[[Christopher Plummer]] \u2013 ''[[Beginners]]'' as Hal Fields'''<ref name=det />\n* [[Kenneth Branagh]] \u2013 ''[[My Week with Marilyn]]'' as [[Laurence Olivier]]\n* [[Albert Brooks]] \u2013 ''[[Drive (2011 film)|Drive]]'' as Bernie Rose\n* [[Ryan Gosling]] \u2013 ''[[Crazy, Stupid, Love]]'' as Jacob Palmer\n* [[Patton Oswalt]] \u2013 ''[[Young Adult (film)|Young Adult]]'' as Matt Freehauf\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Carey Mulligan]] \u2013 ''[[Shame (2011 film)|Shame]]'' as Sissy Sullivan'''<ref name=det />\n* [[B\u00e9r\u00e9nice Bejo]] \u2013 ''[[The Artist (film)|The Artist]]'' as Peppy Miller\n* [[Jessica Chastain]] \u2013 ''[[Take Shelter]]'' as Samantha LaForche\n* [[Vanessa Redgrave]] \u2013 ''[[Coriolanus (film)|Coriolanus]]'' as [[Volumnia]]\n* [[Octavia Spencer]] \u2013 ''[[The Help (film)|The Help]]'' as Minny Jackson\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[Carnage (2011 film)|Carnage]]'''''<ref name=det />\n* ''[[Cedar Rapids (film)|Cedar Rapids]]''\n* ''[[Crazy, Stupid, Love]]''\n* ''[[The Help (film)|The Help]]''\n* ''[[Margin Call (film)|Margin Call]]''\n* ''[[Win Win (film)|Win Win]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Jessica Chastain]] \u2013 ''[[The Help (film)|The Help]]'', ''[[Take Shelter]]'' and ''[[The Tree of Life (film)|The Tree of Life]]'' as Celia Foote, Samantha LaForche, and Mrs. O\u2019Brien'''<ref name=det />\n* [[Felicity Jones]] \u2013 ''[[Like Crazy (2011 film)|Like Crazy]]'' as Anna Maria Gardner\n* [[Melissa McCarthy]] \u2013 ''[[Bridesmaids (2011 film)|Bridesmaids]]'' as Megan Price\n* [[Elizabeth Olsen]] \u2013 ''[[Martha Marcy May Marlene]]'' as Martha\n* [[Shailene Woodley]] \u2013 ''[[The Descendants]]'' as Alexandra King\n\n===Best Screenplay===\n'''''[[Moneyball (film)|Moneyball]]'' \u2013 [[Steven Zaillian]] and [[Aaron Sorkin]]'''<ref name=det />\n* ''[[50/50 (2011 film)|50/50]]'' \u2013 [[Will Reiser]]\n* ''[[The Artist (film)|The 