 Wilson]]\n* [[Benicio del Toro]] \u2013 ''[[Sicario (2015 film)|Sicario]]'' as Alejandro Gillick\n* [[Oscar Isaac]] \u2013 ''[[Ex Machina (film)|Ex Machina]]'' as Nathan Bateman\n* [[Jacob Tremblay]] \u2013 ''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]'' as Jack Newsome\n\n===Best Supporting Actress===\n'''[[Alicia Vikander]] \u2013 ''[[The Danish Girl (film)|The Danish Girl]]'' as [[Gerda Wegener]]'''\n* [[Jennifer Jason Leigh]] \u2013 ''[[The Hateful Eight]]'' as Daisy Domergue\n* [[Cynthia Nixon]] \u2013 ''[[James White (film)|James White]]'' as Gail White\n* [[Kristen Stewart]] \u2013 ''[[Clouds of Sils Maria]]'' as Valentine\n* [[Alicia Vikander]] \u2013 ''[[Ex Machina (film)|Ex Machina]]'' as Ava\n\n===Best Ensemble===\n'''''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'''\n* ''[[The Big Short (film)|The Big Short]]''\n* ''[[The Hateful Eight]]''\n* ''[[Inside Out (2015 film)|Inside Out]]''\n* ''[[Joy (film)|Joy]]''\n\n===Breakthrough Performance===\n'''[[Alicia Vikander]] \u2013 ''[[The Danish Girl (film)|The Danish Girl]]'' and ''[[Ex Machina (film)|Ex Machina]]'''''\n* [[Sean Baker (filmmaker)|Sean Baker]] \u2013 ''[[Tangerine (film)|Tangerine]]'' (director, screenplay)\n* [[Emory Cohen]] \u2013 ''[[Brooklyn (film)|Brooklyn]]'' (actor)\n* [[Bel Powley]] \u2013 ''[[The Diary of a Teenage Girl]]'' (actress)\n* [[Jacob Tremblay]] \u2013 ''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]'' (actor)\n\n===Best Screenplay===\n'''[[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]] and [[Josh Singer]] \u2013 ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'''\n* [[Pete Docter]], [[Meg LeFauve]], and [[Josh Cooley]] \u2013 ''[[Inside Out (2015 film)|Inside Out]]''\n* [[Nick Hornby]] \u2013 ''[[Brooklyn (film)|Brooklyn]]''\n* [[Adam McKay]] and [[Charles Randolph]] \u2013 ''[[The Big Short (film)|The Big Short]]''\n* [[Quentin Tarantino]] \u2013 ''[[The Hateful Eight]]''\n\n===Best Documentary===\n'''''[[Amy (2015 film)|Amy]]'''\n* ''[[Best of Enemies (2015 film)|Best of Enemies]]''\n* ''[[Going Clear (film)|Going Clear: Scientology and the Prison 