edi (2016 film)|Kedi]]''\n* ''[[Step (film)|Step]]''\n* ''[[Strong Island (film)|Strong Island]]''\n* ''[[Whose Streets?]]''\n\n===Best Animated Film===\n'''''[[The Lego Batman Movie]]'''''\n* ''[[Captain Underpants: The First Epic Movie]]''\n* ''[[Cars 3]]''\n* ''[[Coco (2017 film)|Coco]]''\n* ''[[Loving Vincent]]''\n\n===Best Use of Music===\n'''''[[Baby Driver]]'''''\n* ''[[Blade Runner 2049]]''\n* ''[[Good Time (film)|Good Time]]''\n* ''[[Phantom Thread]]''\n* ''[[The Shape of Water]]''\n\n==2018==\n\n===Best Film===\n'''''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eighth Grade]]'''''\n* ''[[First Reformed]]''\n* ''[[Green Book (film)|Green Book]]''\n* ''[[A Quiet Place (film)|A Quiet Place]]''\n* ''[[Roma (2018 film)|Roma]]''\n\n===Best Director===\n'''[[Adam McKay]] \u2013 ''[[Vice (2018 film)|Vice]]'''''\n* [[Bo Burnham]] \u2013 ''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eighth Grade]]''\n* [[Bradley Cooper]] \u2013 ''[[A Star Is Born (2018 film)|A Star Is Born]]''\n* [[Alfonso Cuar\u00f3n]] \u2013 ''[[Roma (2018 film)|Roma]]''\n* [[Paul Schrader]] \u2013 ''[[First Reformed]]''\n\n===Best Actor===\n'''[[Ethan Hawke]] \u2013 ''[[First Reformed]]'' as Reverend Ernst Toller'''\n* [[Christian Bale]] \u2013 ''[[Vice (2018 film)|Vice]]'' as [[Dick Cheney]]\n* [[Bradley Cooper]] \u2013 ''[[A Star Is Born (2018 film)|A Star Is Born]]'' as Jackson Maine\n* [[Rami Malek]] \u2013 ''[[Bohemian Rhapsody (film)|Bohemian Rhapsody]]'' as [[Freddie Mercury]]\n* [[John David Washington]] \u2013 ''[[BlacKkKlansman]]'' as Detective [[Ron Stallworth]]\n\n===Best Actress===\n'''[[Toni Collette]] \u2013 ''[[Hereditary (film)|Hereditary]]'' as Annie Graham'''\n* [[Olivia Colman]] \u2013 ''[[The Favourite (film)|The Favourite]]'' as [[Anne, Queen of Great Britain|Queen Anne]]\n* [[Elsie Fisher]] \u2013 ''[[Eighth Grade (film)|Eighth Grade]]'' as Kayla Day\n* [[Lady Gaga]] \u2013 ''[[A Star Is Born (2018 film)|A Star Is Born]]'' as Ally Maine\n* [[Melissa McCarthy]] \u2013 ''[[Can You Ever Forgive Me? (film)|Can You Ever Fo